<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Reset Password OTP</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .email-header {
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .email-header h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .email-body {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .otp-box {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #f0f4ff;
      color: #0a58ca;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .email-footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }

    strong {
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hello,</p>

      <p>We received a request to reset the password for the account associated with the email address:</p>

      <p><strong><%= email %></strong></p>

      <p>Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to proceed with resetting your password:</p>

      <div class="otp-box"><%= otp %></div>

      <p>This OTP is valid for <strong>1 minute 30 seconds</strong>.</p>

      <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your account remains secure.</p>

      <p>Thank you,<br>
      <strong><%= app %> Team</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= app %>. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
